<li>I'm so sorry for letting you down. You deserve so much better than my behavior.</li>
<li>Please accept my sincerest apologies. I will work to make things right.</li>
<li>I take full responsibility for my mistakes. I am truly sorry for everything.</li>
<li>I cherish our bond, and I'm devastated that I jeopardized it.  I am truly sorry.</li>
